e:T85e,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Amazon CodeWhisperer (Q Developer) better than Devin?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Amazon CodeWhisperer (Q Developer) scores 7.0 overall while Devin scores 7.0. Amazon CodeWhisperer (Q Developer) is best for AWS developers and teams already in AWS ecosystem, while Devin excels for teams wanting autonomous coding agents and complex multi-step tasks."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Amazon CodeWhisperer (Q Developer) or Devin?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Amazon CodeWhisperer (Q Developer) starts at $19/mo and Devin starts at $500/mo. Amazon CodeWhisperer (Q Developer) offers a free plan.  Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Amazon CodeWhisperer (Q Developer) to Devin?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Amazon CodeWhisperer (Q Developer) and Devin support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Amazon CodeWhisperer (Q Developer) vs Devin?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Amazon CodeWhisperer (Q Developer) holds an overall rating of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10. Devin has an overall rating of 7/10 and ease of use score of 6/10. Users praise Amazon CodeWhisperer (Q Developer) for free tier for individuals and Devin for can work autonomously on tasks."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Amazon CodeWhisperer (Q Developer) or Devin?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Amazon CodeWhisperer (Q Developer) for most users based on its overall score and feature set.